---
import WikiLayout from '../../layouts/WikiLayout.astro';
import TableOfContents from '../../components/TableOfContents.astro';
import InfoBox from '../../components/InfoBox.astro';

const pageTitle = "What is Shopis?";

const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: "platform-overview", text: "Platform Overview" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "core-mission", text: "Core Mission" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "key-benefits", text: "Key Benefits" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "how-it-works", text: "How It Works" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "target-users", text: "Who Uses Shopis?" }
];
---

<WikiLayout title={pageTitle}>
  <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">{pageTitle}</h1>
    <div class="flex gap-2">
      <a href="#" class="text-sm px-3 py-1 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800">
        View history
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="text-sm px-3 py-1 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800">
        Discussion
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <TableOfContents headings={headings} />

  <h2 id="platform-overview">Platform Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Shopis is a revolutionary shopping list and grocery management application that transforms how you plan, shop, and manage your purchases. 
    Built with modern technology and user-centric design, Shopis combines artificial intelligence, voice recognition, and barcode scanning 
    to create the most intuitive shopping experience possible.
  </p>
  <p>
    Unlike traditional shopping apps, Shopis goes beyond simple list-making. It's your personal shopping assistant that learns your 
    preferences, suggests items based on your habits, helps you stick to budgets, and ensures you never forget an essential item again.
  </p>

  <div class="my-6 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <img 
      src="https://github.com/ShopListApp/Shopisdisplay/blob/main/images/mockup.jpg?raw=true" 
      alt="Smart shopping with mobile technology"
      class="w-full h-auto"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="p-3 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-800">
      Shopis brings smart technology to everyday shopping, making it more efficient and organized.
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="core-mission">Core Mission</h2>
  <p>
    Our mission is to eliminate the stress and inefficiency from shopping by providing intelligent tools that adapt to your lifestyle. 
    We believe shopping should be quick, organized, and even enjoyable. Shopis empowers users to:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Save time through smart automation and voice commands</li>
    <li>Reduce food waste by better planning and tracking</li>
    <li>Stay within budget with intelligent spending insights</li>
    <li>Collaborate seamlessly with family and friends</li>
    <li>Make informed decisions with purchase history and analytics</li>
  </ul>

  <InfoBox type="success" title="Smart Shopping Revolution">
    Shopis users report saving an average of 2 hours per week on shopping-related tasks and reducing their grocery spending by 15% through better planning and budget tracking.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="key-benefits">Key Benefits</h2>
  <p>
    Shopis offers numerous advantages over traditional shopping methods and basic list apps:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Voice-Powered Convenience</strong>: Add items to your list hands-free while cooking, driving, or multitasking
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Instant Barcode Recognition</strong>: Scan products to add them instantly with accurate names and details
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Intelligent Suggestions</strong>: AI-powered recommendations based on your shopping patterns and preferences
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Real-Time Collaboration</strong>: Share lists with family members and see updates instantly across all devices
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Budget Management</strong>: Set spending goals and track expenses with detailed category breakdowns
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Cross-Platform Sync</strong>: Access your lists from any device - phone, tablet, or computer
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Offline Functionality</strong>: Continue using your lists even without internet connection
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="how-it-works">How It Works</h2>
  <p>
    Shopis simplifies shopping through an intuitive three-step process:
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Create & Organize</strong>: Build your shopping lists using voice commands, barcode scanning, or manual entry. 
      Organize items by categories, stores, or custom groups.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Plan & Budget</strong>: Set budget goals, get price estimates, and receive smart suggestions for meal planning 
      and bulk buying opportunities.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Shop & Track</strong>: Use your organized lists while shopping, check off items as you go, and track your 
      spending in real-time. Review your purchase history and analytics afterward.
    </li>
  </ol>

  <InfoBox type="info" title="Getting Started">
    Ready to try Shopis? Download the app from your device's app store or visit our web application. Creating an account takes less than a minute, and you can start building your first smart shopping list immediately.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="target-users">Who Uses Shopis?</h2>
  <p>
    Shopis is designed for anyone who wants to make their shopping more efficient and organized:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Busy Families</strong>: Parents juggling work and household management who need to coordinate shopping with 
      their partners and keep track of family needs
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Budget-Conscious Shoppers</strong>: Individuals and families looking to control spending and make informed 
      purchasing decisions
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Meal Planners</strong>: People who plan their meals in advance and need organized grocery lists to support 
      their cooking goals
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Students</strong>: College students managing limited budgets who benefit from student discounts and spending 
      tracking features
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Seniors</strong>: Older adults who appreciate voice commands and large, clear interfaces for easier shopping 
      management
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Small Business Owners</strong>: Restaurant owners, caterers, and other business owners who need to manage 
      inventory and supplies efficiently
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Whether you're shopping for groceries, household supplies, or planning special events, Shopis adapts to your specific 
    needs and shopping style.
  </p>
</WikiLayout>
